      • processed

        public void processed(String sourceId,
             String targetId,
             boolean linkExisted,
             String linkId,
             boolean linkWasCreated,
             org.forgerock.openidm.sync.impl.Situation situation,
             org.forgerock.openidm.sync.impl.Action action)
        Handle the processed notification to update the statistics appropriately
        Parameters:
        sourceId - The source id processed, or null if none
        targetId - The target id processed, or null if none
        linkExisted - indication if the link existed before the operation
        linkId - the link identifier, if available. For created links this may not currently be available.
        linkCreated - indication if a new link was created during the operation
        situation - the assessed situation
        action - the action that was processed
